1
00:00:15,060 --> 00:00:18,860
♪Memories of the past are always vivid♪

2
00:00:19,540 --> 00:00:22,340
♪They accompanied me to take every step♪

3
00:00:24,020 --> 00:00:26,380
♪On the road♪

4
00:00:29,260 --> 00:00:33,060
♪Going through heat and cold♪

5
00:00:33,820 --> 00:00:36,900
♪The bumpy journey
has rendered my longing♪

6
00:00:37,780 --> 00:00:40,820
♪Rock solid♪

7
00:00:41,740 --> 00:00:47,420
♪The same moonlight
shines on our shoulders♪

8
00:00:47,980 --> 00:00:51,060
♪Even if we are far away separated♪

9
00:00:51,660 --> 00:00:56,700
♪We are close in our hearts♪

10
00:00:59,860 --> 00:01:01,340
♪The wind blew away the past♪

11
00:01:01,620 --> 00:01:06,860
♪I look for your distant location
on the starry night♪

12
00:01:07,020 --> 00:01:08,460
♪In the ocean of faces♪

13
00:01:08,740 --> 00:01:14,100
♪For you, my heart burns and races♪

14
00:01:14,460 --> 00:01:18,060
♪Despite its turns and twists,
fate is in my hands♪

15
00:01:18,100 --> 00:01:22,060
♪May waiting convert regrets
into a happy ending♪

16
00:01:22,260 --> 00:01:28,220
♪May solitary figures
find right companions♪

17
00:01:28,980 --> 00:01:31,100
♪And become a pair♪

18
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:37,180
=Time Flies and You Are Here=

19
00:01:37,420 --> 00:01:38,980
=Episode 8=

20
00:01:39,120 --> 00:01:40,716
(Chinese mugwort on Dragon Boat Festival
and friends away from me)

21
00:01:44,520 --> 00:01:46,400
(Siqi Hall)

22
00:01:54,040 --> 00:01:55,120
Where are your manners?

23
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:58,319
Your hands.

24
00:02:05,559 --> 00:02:06,120
Hanchen.

25
00:02:06,959 --> 00:02:08,039
Did you forget what you said?

26
00:02:08,759 --> 00:02:09,800
We mustn't alert the opponent.

27
00:02:13,039 --> 00:02:14,000
Momo, do not

28
00:02:14,000 --> 00:02:15,039
be aggravated.

29
00:02:16,000 --> 00:02:17,320
She's just a mere concubine.

30
00:02:17,600 --> 00:02:18,839
She's not capable of anything.

31
00:02:19,520 --> 00:02:21,039
You should get some rest.

32
00:02:22,240 --> 00:02:23,960
Your Highness is right.

33
00:02:24,520 --> 00:02:26,000
She's but a concubine.

34
00:02:26,919 --> 00:02:27,880
In this world,

35
00:02:27,880 --> 00:02:30,199
there are many who
don't know their places.

36
00:02:30,639 --> 00:02:32,639
A concubine may be favoured right now,

37
00:02:33,000 --> 00:02:34,600
and she wants to pursue her studies.

38
00:02:35,240 --> 00:02:36,479
Not long after that,

39
00:02:36,800 --> 00:02:39,360
she's going to covet after
the position as the first wife.

40
00:02:39,679 --> 00:02:40,880
Who knows?

41
00:02:43,160 --> 00:02:44,360
You're right, Zhu Momo.

42
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:46,839
She will not get what she wants.

43
00:02:48,520 --> 00:02:49,880
Continue the learning tomorrow.

44
00:02:56,960 --> 00:02:57,880
Continue.

45
00:03:08,600 --> 00:03:09,479
Did you manage to figure something out?

46
00:03:09,839 --> 00:03:10,720
Yes.

47
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,360
Mother wants me to marry Shen Zhaowen.

48
00:03:12,679 --> 00:03:14,039
We cannot offend Shen Family.

49
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:15,520
Are you going to beg Shen Yan?

50
00:03:15,839 --> 00:03:16,839
Who said I'm going to beg him?

51
00:03:17,160 --> 00:03:17,919
We're exchanging terms.

52
00:03:18,639 --> 00:03:19,559
By the way, Mr. Liangji,

53
00:03:20,039 --> 00:03:21,320
are the gifts to welcome
Xiaoman's return

54
00:03:21,320 --> 00:03:22,199
prepared?

55
00:03:23,320 --> 00:03:24,839
I'll select some goods
from the inventory.

56
00:03:25,119 --> 00:03:26,320
I'm not sure about the specifications.

57
00:03:26,320 --> 00:03:27,639
The specifications to marry a wife.

58
00:03:28,399 --> 00:03:30,199
I'll return with her when the day comes.

59
00:03:31,520 --> 00:03:32,039
Also,

60
00:03:33,559 --> 00:03:34,759
fetch me some ointment.

61
00:03:36,199 --> 00:03:37,080
I'm going to check on her.

62
00:03:38,119 --> 00:03:38,600
All right.

63
00:03:41,639 --> 00:03:42,240
Hanchen.

64
00:03:42,919 --> 00:03:44,800
Although we owe Xiaoman big time,

65
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,520
you need to bear a sense of propriety.

66
00:03:46,839 --> 00:03:47,360
You mustn't

67
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:48,839
treat her like the first wife.

68
00:03:49,399 --> 00:03:51,119
If such a hope is evoked in her,

69
00:03:51,399 --> 00:03:52,559
it's only going to harm her.

70
00:03:54,479 --> 00:03:55,199
There are things

71
00:03:55,759 --> 00:03:56,759
I owe her.

72
00:03:57,520 --> 00:03:59,559
Whatever she seeks, within my means,

73
00:04:00,399 --> 00:04:01,320
I'll fulfil them.

74
00:04:02,240 --> 00:04:03,039
Do you understand?

75
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:18,200
The moment you can rely on a man

76
00:04:18,640 --> 00:04:19,799
is when sows are able to climb trees.

77
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:24,679
Sows are able to climb tree?

78
00:04:25,359 --> 00:04:26,559
Climb a tree and show me.

79
00:04:27,559 --> 00:04:28,440
What are you doing here?

80
00:04:33,760 --> 00:04:34,640
Show me your hands.

81
00:04:35,519 --> 00:04:36,359
I'm applying the medication for you.

82
00:04:42,079 --> 00:04:42,760
Your hands.

83
00:04:55,040 --> 00:04:56,480
Did you come just to do this?

84
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:57,640
Yes.

85
00:04:58,320 --> 00:04:59,600
You're such a fool.

86
00:05:00,320 --> 00:05:01,720
You should butter Zhu Momo up.

87
00:05:01,720 --> 00:05:02,559
Say something flattering.

88
00:05:03,320 --> 00:05:04,839
You'd willingly go through
the troubles she caused you.

89
00:05:05,920 --> 00:05:06,920
She was wrong.

90
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,279
Why should I compromise?

91
00:05:08,519 --> 00:05:09,440
Did you know

92
00:05:09,760 --> 00:05:11,480
for married women to return
to the academy,

93
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:12,920
they'd turn into a laughing stock?

94
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,200
A laughing stock?

95
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,920
Pursuing studies will be made a joke,

96
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,679
but attending to
trivial matters of the house

97
00:05:20,679 --> 00:05:21,880
is more important?

98
00:05:22,839 --> 00:05:24,320
Both of us are married by contract.

99
00:05:24,760 --> 00:05:25,399
After two years,

100
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,799
we no longer have anything
to do with each other.

101
00:05:27,799 --> 00:05:29,359
If I'm not concerned of
my future right now,

102
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,079
after two years,

103
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,839
do you want me to end up

104
00:05:33,079 --> 00:05:34,559
from one backyard to another?

105
00:05:36,200 --> 00:05:38,839
We shall go our own ways
after two years?

106
00:05:41,399 --> 00:05:41,959
Fine.

107
00:05:42,760 --> 00:05:43,880
Forget about the academy.

108
00:05:44,880 --> 00:05:45,320
You...

109
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,239
Wick was right.

110
00:05:49,880 --> 00:05:50,760
The moment you can rely on a man

111
00:05:51,200 --> 00:05:52,600
is when sows are able to climb trees.

112
00:06:31,300 --> 00:06:33,940
(Qu Yuan's Poem)

113
00:06:49,720 --> 00:06:50,600
Congwen.

114
00:06:53,760 --> 00:06:54,760
What are you doing here?

115
00:06:58,720 --> 00:06:59,519
You're dismissed.

116
00:07:03,119 --> 00:07:04,679
I heard about Xiaoman

117
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:05,880
and His Highness's incident.

118
00:07:06,440 --> 00:07:07,839
Xiaoman was absent
from the academy today.

119
00:07:08,600 --> 00:07:10,279
I figured something
must have happened.

120
00:07:10,760 --> 00:07:11,559
I came to see

121
00:07:11,799 --> 00:07:13,000
if there's anything I can do to help.

122
00:07:14,920 --> 00:07:16,239
On the day of Xiaoman's wedding,

123
00:07:17,119 --> 00:07:18,760
I sent someone to deliver
a message to you

124
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,760
at the brothel.

125
00:07:20,519 --> 00:07:21,799
However, you did not show up.

126
00:07:23,200 --> 00:07:24,519
I was unaware of this matter.

127
00:07:24,799 --> 00:07:25,480
Well,

128
00:07:25,480 --> 00:07:26,559
it no longer matters now.

129
00:07:27,200 --> 00:07:28,399
Xiaoman is married now.

130
00:07:29,480 --> 00:07:31,320
Besides, she has a huge
trouble to deal with right now.

131
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,720
Zhu Momo came from the capital.

132
00:07:34,279 --> 00:07:35,320
She forbade Xiaoman from
pursuing her studies.

133
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,760
I wanted to take her

134
00:07:37,760 --> 00:07:39,200
to meet Teacher Liu on
the day of examination

135
00:07:39,359 --> 00:07:40,720
and seek help from Teacher Liu.

136
00:07:41,839 --> 00:07:42,799
However, it seems like...

137
00:07:44,040 --> 00:07:45,119
Even Teacher Liu wouldn't
be able to help her.

138
00:07:45,519 --> 00:07:46,359
At this point,

139
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:48,279
Principal Yang is the only
one that could help her.

140
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:50,559
On the day of the examination,

141
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:51,839
try your best to help Xiaoman

142
00:07:51,839 --> 00:07:53,200
take the test at the academy.

143
00:07:53,880 --> 00:07:55,079
I'll submit Xiaoman's test papers

144
00:07:55,079 --> 00:07:56,119
to Principal Yang Chidao.

145
00:07:57,200 --> 00:07:59,279
Principal Yang is highly respectable
in Wujiang Prefecture.

146
00:08:00,119 --> 00:08:01,799
Back at the palace,
Commandery Prince of Julu

147
00:08:01,799 --> 00:08:03,160
was tutored by Principal Yang.

148
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,200
In the whole of Wujiang Prefecture,

149
00:08:05,679 --> 00:08:07,399
Principal Yang is the only one who can

150
00:08:08,000 --> 00:08:08,920
control Zhao Xiaoqian.

151
00:08:10,000 --> 00:08:10,839
Leave it to me.

152
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:13,440
All you have to do is bring
Xiaoman to the academy.

153
00:08:17,480 --> 00:08:18,119
What's the matter?

154
00:08:18,880 --> 00:08:19,600
Nothing.

155
00:08:19,799 --> 00:08:20,760
I shall thank you

156
00:08:20,920 --> 00:08:21,959
on Xiaoman's behalf, Congwen.

157
00:08:23,440 --> 00:08:24,399
I'm going to

158
00:08:24,399 --> 00:08:25,559
deliver a message to
Commandery Prince's Mansion right now.

159
00:08:28,940 --> 00:08:32,860
(Commandery Prince's Mansion)

160
00:08:35,760 --> 00:08:36,479
Lady.

161
00:08:39,799 --> 00:08:40,440
Since you've

162
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,479
gained His Highness's
grace to return home,

163
00:08:42,679 --> 00:08:44,039
you should enjoy your time there.

164
00:08:44,359 --> 00:08:45,239
I informed

165
00:08:45,239 --> 00:08:46,599
Zhu Momo about this.

166
00:08:46,799 --> 00:08:48,559
There's no need for you
to return urgently.

167
00:08:48,760 --> 00:08:49,919
Spent some time with your family.

168
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:51,880
The gifts

169
00:08:51,880 --> 00:08:53,359
are all packed up by Mr. Liangji.

170
00:08:53,359 --> 00:08:54,400
Lady Xie, hurry up.

171
00:08:55,200 --> 00:08:55,760
I'm coming.

172
00:08:57,520 --> 00:08:58,840
I'll return as soon as possible.

173
00:09:13,000 --> 00:09:14,479
Lady Xie did not bring
any attendants along.

174
00:09:14,679 --> 00:09:16,239
Xie Family will be troubled

175
00:09:16,239 --> 00:09:17,159
to carry the gift on their own.

176
00:09:17,840 --> 00:09:19,679
Tag along and help with the goods.

177
00:09:19,679 --> 00:09:20,080
Yes.

178
00:09:25,799 --> 00:09:26,400
Stop the carriage.

179
00:09:30,239 --> 00:09:31,159
Go ahead.

180
00:09:31,919 --> 00:09:33,080
My sister will be waiting for me here.

181
00:09:33,799 --> 00:09:34,799
Zhu Momo ordered for us

182
00:09:35,200 --> 00:09:36,400
to send you right to your door step.

183
00:09:37,119 --> 00:09:37,880
Besides, there's a carriage of goods...

184
00:09:37,880 --> 00:09:38,479
How about this?

185
00:09:39,000 --> 00:09:39,919
Go ahead and return.

186
00:09:40,599 --> 00:09:42,440
My sister and I are going
to buy some baked bread.

187
00:09:42,760 --> 00:09:44,039
It's my father's favourite.

188
00:09:44,039 --> 00:09:44,640
After that,

189
00:09:44,760 --> 00:09:46,359
my sister and I will return home
on her carriage.

190
00:09:47,119 --> 00:09:47,559
All right.

191
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:50,119
I would like some baked bread, too.

192
00:09:50,599 --> 00:09:51,520
You should leave first.

193
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:52,599
After Xiaoman and I are done,

194
00:09:52,599 --> 00:09:53,440
we will come to you.

195
00:09:54,559 --> 00:09:55,400
Go on.

196
00:09:55,400 --> 00:09:56,440
My mother could barely wait.

197
00:10:07,239 --> 00:10:07,760
Let's hurry.

198
00:10:07,760 --> 00:10:08,559
Otherwise, we wouldn't make it.

199
00:10:09,239 --> 00:10:10,119
You haven't told me

200
00:10:10,119 --> 00:10:11,599
why I should take
the examination at the academy.

201
00:10:11,719 --> 00:10:12,599
It doesn't matter.

202
00:10:12,799 --> 00:10:13,719
I'll not cause you harm.

203
00:10:14,799 --> 00:10:15,599
Where's our carriage?

204
00:10:16,840 --> 00:10:17,559
It's arriving soon.

205
00:10:18,400 --> 00:10:19,119
Give it a moment.

206
00:10:19,980 --> 00:10:21,260
(Brothel)

207
00:10:21,320 --> 00:10:21,599
Get on.

208
00:10:21,599 --> 00:10:22,280
Gnaw on it.

209
00:10:22,440 --> 00:10:23,559
Give it a bite.

210
00:10:23,679 --> 00:10:24,440
Bite on it.

211
00:10:24,719 --> 00:10:25,679
Bite on it.

212
00:10:25,840 --> 00:10:26,599
Yes, attack.

213
00:10:26,599 --> 00:10:27,159
Bite it.

214
00:10:27,599 --> 00:10:28,320
Come on.

215
00:10:29,039 --> 00:10:29,719
Zhao Xiaoqian,

216
00:10:29,840 --> 00:10:30,679
what happens if you lose?

217
00:10:31,000 --> 00:10:32,359
It's your call

218
00:10:33,320 --> 00:10:34,559
under one condition.

219
00:10:34,719 --> 00:10:36,479
You're troubling me
with the matters of your family.

220
00:10:36,719 --> 00:10:37,960
You insist to play a bet with me.

221
00:10:38,599 --> 00:10:40,440
If it wasn't for your brother's sake,

222
00:10:41,479 --> 00:10:42,479
I couldn't be bothered.

223
00:10:42,479 --> 00:10:43,200
Shut up.

224
00:10:43,960 --> 00:10:44,719
If it wasn't for you,

225
00:10:44,719 --> 00:10:45,799
things wouldn't have ended up this way.

226
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:48,239
Don't worry though.

227
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:50,000
I'm one to concede defeat.

228
00:10:50,919 --> 00:10:51,599
Same goes to you.

229
00:10:52,080 --> 00:10:52,479
Attack.

230
00:10:52,479 --> 00:10:53,039
That's right.

231
00:10:53,039 --> 00:10:53,799
Jin Guo, advance.

232
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:55,200
Advance.

233
00:10:55,599 --> 00:10:56,479
Ming Guan.

234
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:57,840
Good job!

235
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:02,840
Zhao Xiaoqian.

236
00:11:02,960 --> 00:11:03,559
It's your turn

237
00:11:03,799 --> 00:11:04,919
to obey me now.

238
00:11:06,840 --> 00:11:07,479
Come on.

239
00:11:08,960 --> 00:11:09,479
Come on.

240
00:11:17,960 --> 00:11:18,599
Shen Yan.

241
00:11:19,679 --> 00:11:20,719
Do not carry this too far.

242
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:22,039
Are you refusing me?

243
00:11:22,719 --> 00:11:23,679
Fine.

244
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:25,479
The one who said he'd concede defeat

245
00:11:25,960 --> 00:11:26,719
wasn't me anyway.

246
00:11:28,200 --> 00:11:28,679
Let's go.

247
00:11:29,440 --> 00:11:29,960
Hold up.

248
00:11:33,239 --> 00:11:34,039
I concur.

249
00:11:38,440 --> 00:11:39,679
I admit my defeat this time.

250
00:11:40,679 --> 00:11:41,840
However, if you failed to

251
00:11:41,840 --> 00:11:43,119
accomplish the task I ordered you to,

252
00:11:43,719 --> 00:11:45,400
the conflict between us
will not be easily

253
00:11:45,400 --> 00:11:46,320
resolved at the racing ground.

254
00:11:47,559 --> 00:11:48,719
I know what the old servant of yours

255
00:11:48,719 --> 00:11:49,840
is thinking.

256
00:11:50,400 --> 00:11:52,559
She wants to make me your relative.

257
00:11:53,559 --> 00:11:54,479
Dream on.

258
00:11:55,080 --> 00:11:56,840
If my sister is married to you,

259
00:11:56,960 --> 00:11:58,400
my name is no longer Shen Yan.

260
00:12:01,159 --> 00:12:01,599
Zhao,

261
00:12:01,599 --> 00:12:02,799
what are you doing over there?

262
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:03,960
Hurry up and get ready.

263
00:12:04,599 --> 00:12:05,440
Leave

264
00:12:05,719 --> 00:12:07,239
the rest to me, Master Shen.

265
00:12:21,119 --> 00:12:21,799
We'll see.

266
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:28,599
Hurry up.

267
00:12:28,960 --> 00:12:29,919
We're running out of time.

268
00:12:30,280 --> 00:12:30,840
The class is commencing.

269
00:12:31,000 --> 00:12:31,840
We're running late. Hurry.

270
00:12:32,840 --> 00:12:33,280
Hurry.

271
00:12:38,580 --> 00:12:42,460
(Jingnv Pavilion)

272
00:12:43,039 --> 00:12:43,559
Xiaoman.

273
00:12:45,880 --> 00:12:46,479
Don't worry.

274
00:12:46,960 --> 00:12:47,840
No one would find out.

275
00:12:48,359 --> 00:12:49,760
This is the best solution for now.

276
00:12:49,880 --> 00:12:50,760
Don't think about anything else.

277
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:51,599
Just take the test.

278
00:12:52,039 --> 00:12:53,400
Don't worry about the rest.

279
00:12:53,640 --> 00:12:54,320
Leave it to me.

280
00:12:56,559 --> 00:12:57,359
We shall head on inside then.

281
00:12:57,359 --> 00:12:57,840
Let's go.

282
00:12:58,220 --> 00:13:01,500
(Jingnv Pavilion)

283
00:13:14,479 --> 00:13:15,760
Return to your seats.

284
00:13:22,039 --> 00:13:22,919
What is she doing here?

285
00:13:24,880 --> 00:13:26,200
She's shameless.

286
00:13:27,599 --> 00:13:28,520
Cut it out.

287
00:13:38,840 --> 00:13:40,520
All right. Everyone is present.

288
00:13:41,159 --> 00:13:42,000
Fellow ladies,

289
00:13:42,400 --> 00:13:43,159
you may begin.

290
00:14:09,799 --> 00:14:10,320
Hongsu.

291
00:14:11,080 --> 00:14:11,640
Hongsu.

292
00:14:13,520 --> 00:14:14,239
What's the matter?

293
00:14:14,239 --> 00:14:15,479
Has Lady Xie returned?

294
00:14:15,799 --> 00:14:16,520
No.

295
00:14:16,679 --> 00:14:17,599
I witnessed with my own eyes.

296
00:14:17,799 --> 00:14:19,080
Lady Xie did not return home.

297
00:14:19,359 --> 00:14:20,559
She went straight to Bailu Academy.

298
00:14:22,280 --> 00:14:23,239
Head to the academy

299
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,440
and inform master about this.

300
00:14:24,760 --> 00:14:26,479
Don't let master make an empty trip.

301
00:14:26,799 --> 00:14:27,280
All right.

302
00:14:39,239 --> 00:14:39,799
Hongsu.

303
00:14:40,400 --> 00:14:41,200
Why are you in a daze?

304
00:14:49,719 --> 00:14:51,080
You look troubled.

305
00:14:51,679 --> 00:14:52,320
Don't worry.

306
00:14:53,080 --> 00:14:54,359
Lady Xie

307
00:14:54,799 --> 00:14:56,119
will not be able to last any longer.

308
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:57,799
Master doesn't care about her.

309
00:14:58,000 --> 00:14:59,680
She will be gone in a few days.

310
00:14:59,960 --> 00:15:01,799
By then, once we return to the capital,

311
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:04,640
great fortune and wealth
will be awaiting you.

312
00:15:05,479 --> 00:15:06,159
Momo.

313
00:15:14,700 --> 00:15:17,340
(Delicacy Restaurant)

314
00:15:19,159 --> 00:15:20,359
This bowl of quail soup is horrendous.

315
00:15:22,000 --> 00:15:23,760
It's nothing compared to the
one from Taiping Tavern.

316
00:15:24,239 --> 00:15:25,119
In my opinion,

317
00:15:25,280 --> 00:15:26,119
it's time to switch out

318
00:15:26,119 --> 00:15:27,080
the chef of Delicacy Restaurant.

319
00:15:28,159 --> 00:15:29,159
You should recruit
my family's chef instead.

320
00:15:29,599 --> 00:15:31,719
My mother hired the chef all
the way from Hangzhou for me.

321
00:15:31,880 --> 00:15:33,599
His dish, West Lake Fish in
Vinegar Gravy is extraordinary.

322
00:15:33,599 --> 00:15:35,719
Are you attempting to
hog things from home?

323
00:15:36,640 --> 00:15:37,239
Bring it over.

324
00:15:38,520 --> 00:15:39,280
That's enough.

325
00:15:41,039 --> 00:15:41,599
By the way,

326
00:15:42,159 --> 00:15:42,799
Zhao,

327
00:15:43,520 --> 00:15:45,039
what did you promise Shen Yan?

328
00:15:45,799 --> 00:15:46,719
After speaking to him,

329
00:15:46,719 --> 00:15:47,919
he exerted arrogance.

330
00:15:47,919 --> 00:15:49,080
It's irritating to watch.

331
00:15:49,440 --> 00:15:50,799
Try addressing me by Zhao once more.

332
00:15:51,359 --> 00:15:52,080
I was wrong.

333
00:15:52,359 --> 00:15:53,119
Brother Zhao.

334
00:15:56,080 --> 00:15:57,840
What did you promise him?

335
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:00,919
It's none of your concern.

336
00:16:01,520 --> 00:16:02,880
A great man knows when to yield.

337
00:16:03,280 --> 00:16:04,760
I'm making a compromise for my wife.

338
00:16:04,840 --> 00:16:05,559
Leave it.

339
00:16:09,559 --> 00:16:10,320
Yes.

340
00:16:11,200 --> 00:16:12,679
Don't you find it strange?

341
00:16:13,719 --> 00:16:14,559
Zhu Momo

342
00:16:14,840 --> 00:16:16,039
wouldn't listen to a
single word you say.

343
00:16:16,239 --> 00:16:17,880
Why would she listen to Shen Yan?

344
00:16:17,880 --> 00:16:19,159
Zhu Momo wants Hanchen

345
00:16:19,159 --> 00:16:20,039
to marry Shen Zhaowen.

346
00:16:20,880 --> 00:16:21,440
Shen Yan

347
00:16:21,440 --> 00:16:22,840
is the biological brother
of Shen Zhaowen.

348
00:16:23,320 --> 00:16:24,359
To Zhu Momo,

349
00:16:24,799 --> 00:16:26,080
Shen Yan is Hanchen's brother-in-law.

350
00:16:26,960 --> 00:16:28,479
Zhu Momo may offend anyone

351
00:16:28,719 --> 00:16:29,840
but the Shen Family.

352
00:16:30,280 --> 00:16:31,479
If Shen Yan claims that

353
00:16:31,719 --> 00:16:32,880
his sister enjoys studying,

354
00:16:33,119 --> 00:16:33,760
and hopes the same

355
00:16:33,760 --> 00:16:35,280
for the rest of the women of the family,

356
00:16:35,559 --> 00:16:36,080
that way,

357
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:37,559
Zhu Momo will no longer stop

358
00:16:37,559 --> 00:16:38,440
Xiaoman from pursuing her studies.

359
00:16:38,880 --> 00:16:39,640
Do you understand?

360
00:16:41,039 --> 00:16:42,719
Not bad, Zhao Xiaoqian.

361
00:16:43,599 --> 00:16:46,000
You have a way of messing
with the elders.

362
00:16:46,799 --> 00:16:47,719
Please enlighten me.

363
00:16:47,719 --> 00:16:49,799
I'll be able to deal
with my father then.

364
00:16:50,479 --> 00:16:51,000
Master.

365
00:16:55,520 --> 00:16:56,320
Lady Xie did not return home.

366
00:16:56,320 --> 00:16:57,559
She went straight to Bailu Academy.

367
00:17:04,000 --> 00:17:04,520
Hanchen.

368
00:17:06,880 --> 00:17:08,479
Wait, we're not finished yet.

369
00:17:09,980 --> 00:17:13,980
(Jingnv Pavilion)

370
00:17:16,359 --> 00:17:17,000
Your Highness.

371
00:17:17,400 --> 00:17:18,319
This is the academy,

372
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,959
not the Commandery Prince's Mansion.

373
00:17:21,839 --> 00:17:22,640
Zhao Xiaoqian.

374
00:17:24,040 --> 00:17:24,719
What's going on?

375
00:17:28,119 --> 00:17:29,599
They are all maidens of nobility.

376
00:17:29,839 --> 00:17:30,839
If you barge in,

377
00:17:31,040 --> 00:17:31,880
it'd be inappropriate.

378
00:17:33,319 --> 00:17:34,839
You're secretly dating my concubine.

379
00:17:35,560 --> 00:17:36,520
Is that appropriate?

380
00:17:37,920 --> 00:17:39,839
You may treat her as whoever you want.

381
00:17:40,239 --> 00:17:41,199
However, this is the academy.

382
00:17:41,560 --> 00:17:42,760
She's just a student.

383
00:17:43,479 --> 00:17:44,680
Your claims of dating
in secret are baseless.

384
00:17:45,599 --> 00:17:46,760
How did he manage to find me here?

385
00:17:51,000 --> 00:17:52,839
One must keep calm in order
to accomplish great things.

386
00:17:56,040 --> 00:17:57,160
Are you admitting

387
00:17:57,520 --> 00:17:59,040
to dating Xie Xiaoman in secret?

388
00:18:00,040 --> 00:18:01,319
Nothing is going on between both of us.

389
00:18:01,680 --> 00:18:02,839
I just want to help her.

390
00:18:03,479 --> 00:18:04,160
For what purpose?

391
00:18:04,839 --> 00:18:05,439
For her to pursue studies.

392
00:18:28,880 --> 00:18:30,959
I completed half of the discourse.

393
00:18:31,479 --> 00:18:32,760
I have yet to complete the rest.

394
00:18:33,599 --> 00:18:34,599
I'm sorry to let you down.

395
00:18:48,359 --> 00:18:48,880
Hanchen.

396
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:53,880
Let go.

397
00:18:54,400 --> 00:18:55,000
Let go.

398
00:19:02,119 --> 00:19:03,000
Are you done?

399
00:19:03,400 --> 00:19:04,199
Thank you.

400
00:19:04,760 --> 00:19:05,640
I did my best.

401
00:19:10,040 --> 00:19:11,000
Why didn't you tell me

402
00:19:11,479 --> 00:19:12,400
about heading to the academy?

403
00:19:12,920 --> 00:19:14,239
Did you think I wouldn't
be able to help you?

404
00:19:16,479 --> 00:19:17,040
Say something.

405
00:19:17,479 --> 00:19:17,959
Yes.

406
00:19:21,199 --> 00:19:22,839
Did you think he will be
able to help you instead?

407
00:19:23,520 --> 00:19:24,640
He's just a mere scholar.

408
00:19:25,160 --> 00:19:26,760
Are you underestimating me
or overestimating him?

409
00:19:27,040 --> 00:19:27,599
My apologies.

410
00:19:30,599 --> 00:19:31,160
Fine.

411
00:19:32,000 --> 00:19:32,760
Xie Xiaoman.

412
00:19:33,439 --> 00:19:34,400
Keep this in mind.

413
00:19:34,680 --> 00:19:35,839
I'm your husband.

414
00:19:36,599 --> 00:19:37,400
Send her home.

415
00:19:38,000 --> 00:19:39,280
Let's go, Lady Xie.

416
00:19:45,839 --> 00:19:46,959
Finish your article.

417
00:19:48,280 --> 00:19:49,000
Congwen.

418
00:19:49,920 --> 00:19:50,760
This is their family matter.

419
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:52,040
Congwen,

420
00:19:52,680 --> 00:19:53,400
I'll be fine.

421
00:19:55,680 --> 00:19:56,199
Xiaoman.

422
00:19:59,199 --> 00:20:00,280
I must speak to you.

423
00:20:13,599 --> 00:20:14,719
Did you think by marrying you,

424
00:20:15,479 --> 00:20:18,000
I have to submit to you completely?

425
00:20:32,760 --> 00:20:35,239
Qu Yuan sang of the
two goddesses of Xiang.

426
00:20:35,680 --> 00:20:37,479
They were transfigured
into divine beings.

427
00:20:37,479 --> 00:20:40,160
They promised to meet by the Lake
of Dongting as the wind blows.

428
00:20:40,520 --> 00:20:42,040
It was a moment of liberation

429
00:20:42,400 --> 00:20:44,119
that the lovers lived for.

430
00:20:45,520 --> 00:20:47,000
She used two of the
Nine Songs of Qu Yuan,

431
00:20:47,000 --> 00:20:48,199
"God of the Xiang" and
"Lady of the Xiang"

432
00:20:48,199 --> 00:20:49,959
to express the virtues of a woman.

433
00:20:51,439 --> 00:20:52,839
That's impressive.

434
00:20:53,760 --> 00:20:54,839
If she was a man,

435
00:20:55,520 --> 00:20:58,119
she may be able to challenge your work.

436
00:20:58,479 --> 00:21:00,359
It's a rarity for a woman
to be able to do so.

437
00:21:01,280 --> 00:21:02,479
As women,

438
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:05,479
certain things are beyond your control.

439
00:21:07,520 --> 00:21:08,400
I understand

440
00:21:08,839 --> 00:21:11,119
you value your school mates.

441
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:12,839
I'm her senior.

442
00:21:13,280 --> 00:21:15,199
It's my obligation to help my juniors.

443
00:21:16,239 --> 00:21:17,040
Besides,

444
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:19,439
I'm indebted to her parents.

445
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:22,760
It's customary to help one of your own.

446
00:21:23,160 --> 00:21:26,040
A grateful man is a man of honour.

447
00:21:26,520 --> 00:21:28,959
However, you're not her husband.

448
00:21:29,160 --> 00:21:30,400
Involving yourself in
helping her constantly

449
00:21:31,000 --> 00:21:32,239
violates tradition and customs.

450
00:21:34,760 --> 00:21:37,000
You seem intelligent,

451
00:21:37,280 --> 00:21:38,880
yet you often engage in folly.

452
00:21:39,520 --> 00:21:42,160
I'm not going to intervene.

453
00:21:43,000 --> 00:21:44,439
You need to figure it out yourself.

454
00:21:44,839 --> 00:21:46,479
If you were Commandery Prince of Julu,

455
00:21:46,959 --> 00:21:48,520
what will you do?

456
00:21:55,040 --> 00:21:56,000
I understand.

457
00:22:12,359 --> 00:22:14,719
Deliver this article
to Commandery Prince of Julu.

458
00:22:15,000 --> 00:22:15,479
Yes, sir.

459
00:22:24,280 --> 00:22:25,640
I read your article.

460
00:22:26,239 --> 00:22:26,839
First class.

461
00:22:28,000 --> 00:22:29,959
Li Su delivered the text to
Principal Yang.

462
00:22:30,359 --> 00:22:32,400
I believe he'd deem it
excellent as well.

463
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,280
Are you saying that

464
00:22:36,000 --> 00:22:37,359
Principal Yang would give me a hand?

465
00:22:40,439 --> 00:22:41,520
As the saying goes,

466
00:22:42,239 --> 00:22:43,439
nothing is more valuable

467
00:22:43,599 --> 00:22:44,680
than studies.

468
00:22:45,599 --> 00:22:46,760
However, the society believes

469
00:22:47,520 --> 00:22:48,760
it's pointless for women to be educated.

470
00:22:49,160 --> 00:22:50,680
Women are forced to cultivate
homemaking skills

471
00:22:51,000 --> 00:22:52,160
in order to marry a good man.

472
00:22:53,719 --> 00:22:55,239
Both of us are women

473
00:22:55,239 --> 00:22:56,439
who sought education and knowledge.

474
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,520
However, we're obstructed by norms

475
00:22:58,520 --> 00:22:59,520
and criticism of the society.

476
00:22:59,839 --> 00:23:01,040
It's unfair.

477
00:23:03,239 --> 00:23:03,959
Honestly,

478
00:23:04,760 --> 00:23:06,280
when my parents asked me

479
00:23:07,239 --> 00:23:08,640
what am I studying for,

480
00:23:09,040 --> 00:23:10,880
before I could come to a realisation,

481
00:23:12,599 --> 00:23:13,760
I was married off.

482
00:23:14,760 --> 00:23:16,359
I already possess

483
00:23:16,640 --> 00:23:17,920
a wealthy and comfortable life.

484
00:23:18,439 --> 00:23:19,760
What's the point of pursuing studies?

485
00:23:20,760 --> 00:23:22,280
The title of your article

486
00:23:22,520 --> 00:23:23,760
evoked some thoughts in me.

487
00:23:25,040 --> 00:23:28,000
If women are literate and educated,

488
00:23:28,319 --> 00:23:31,040
that would indicate the flourishing
of education and arts.

489
00:23:31,400 --> 00:23:35,119
A legacy will be formed
for generations to come.

490
00:23:38,599 --> 00:23:39,160
Bravo.

491
00:23:40,119 --> 00:23:40,920
I'm thirsty.

492
00:23:44,439 --> 00:23:45,560
Lady Xie

493
00:23:45,560 --> 00:23:46,760
is pretty brilliant.

494
00:23:47,119 --> 00:23:48,160
What does it mean?

495
00:23:48,400 --> 00:23:50,160
For all knowledgeable bureaucrats,

496
00:23:50,319 --> 00:23:50,920
they deserve

497
00:23:50,920 --> 00:23:52,760
a woman of equal calibre as a wife

498
00:23:53,199 --> 00:23:54,280
in order to advance civilisation.

499
00:23:55,640 --> 00:23:56,680
Not bad at all.

500
00:23:56,880 --> 00:23:57,800
Impressive.

501
00:23:57,959 --> 00:23:59,079
The current sovereign
promotes culture and literature.

502
00:23:59,199 --> 00:24:01,319
Cultivation of respectable scholars
has been ongoing for centuries.

503
00:24:02,040 --> 00:24:02,959
The talents produced

504
00:24:03,359 --> 00:24:04,560
could surpass both
Han and Tang Dynasty

505
00:24:04,719 --> 00:24:06,439
at their prime.

506
00:24:07,319 --> 00:24:08,000
However,

507
00:24:08,880 --> 00:24:10,920
women of such calibre are rare.

508
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:13,599
If a woman is proficient literature

509
00:24:13,680 --> 00:24:14,439
and composition,

510
00:24:14,920 --> 00:24:16,719
the advancement of culture and arts

511
00:24:16,959 --> 00:24:18,079
will surpass any dynasty

512
00:24:18,079 --> 00:24:19,239
in history

513
00:24:19,520 --> 00:24:20,640
without a single thread of regret.

514
00:24:24,560 --> 00:24:26,000
Ziyan, you're impressive as usual.

515
00:24:26,920 --> 00:24:28,280
You're knowledgeable.

516
00:24:28,280 --> 00:24:28,880
Look.

517
00:24:29,040 --> 00:24:30,239
The government values
scepticism and discernment.

518
00:24:30,319 --> 00:24:31,400
Scholars were cultivated
over the century.

519
00:24:32,000 --> 00:24:34,800
The birth and progress of talents will
surpass Han Dynasty and our forefathers.

520
00:24:35,839 --> 00:24:37,239
Women of wisdom

521
00:24:38,359 --> 00:24:39,599
are indeed rare.

522
00:24:46,119 --> 00:24:47,719
You understood it yourself.

523
00:24:48,000 --> 00:24:49,479
There's no need for me
to explain further.

524
00:24:50,400 --> 00:24:52,239
Whether Principal Yang permits
you to return to school or not,

525
00:24:52,839 --> 00:24:54,680
I hope you will never stop studying,

526
00:24:54,959 --> 00:24:56,319
speculating and reasoning.

527
00:24:57,119 --> 00:24:58,119
Beauty will not last.

528
00:24:58,439 --> 00:24:59,400
Delicacies and luxuries

529
00:24:59,719 --> 00:25:01,560
are just physical necessities.

530
00:25:02,239 --> 00:25:03,800
Only conviction and thoughts

531
00:25:04,119 --> 00:25:06,160
will guide you for
the rest of your life.

532
00:25:07,599 --> 00:25:10,199
Peril can only be evaded through
constant improvement and progress.

533
00:25:12,079 --> 00:25:12,959
I understand.

534
00:25:13,479 --> 00:25:14,760
I'll keep your words
engraved in my heart.

535
00:25:18,199 --> 00:25:19,079
If it's possible,

536
00:25:19,719 --> 00:25:20,719
I would like to

537
00:25:20,959 --> 00:25:22,760
be a wise teacher like you

538
00:25:23,079 --> 00:25:25,079
to guide and enlighten others.

539
00:25:30,620 --> 00:25:32,300
(Fengxue Pavilion)

540
00:25:32,439 --> 00:25:33,599
This is a splendid discourse.

541
00:25:34,400 --> 00:25:36,319
She dreams to become a female tutor.

542
00:25:41,680 --> 00:25:42,920
Does she really enjoy reading so much?

543
00:25:44,400 --> 00:25:45,319
To each their own.

544
00:25:45,680 --> 00:25:46,959
Just like you enjoy
archery and horse riding.

545
00:25:48,000 --> 00:25:48,680
Why?

546
00:25:50,760 --> 00:25:51,880
To understand the truth.

547
00:25:53,239 --> 00:25:54,560
She's unreasonable,

548
00:25:55,119 --> 00:25:56,280
what's the truth she seeks?

549
00:26:04,479 --> 00:26:05,560
Ban Zhao was educated

550
00:26:06,280 --> 00:26:07,520
and produced the Book of Han.

551
00:26:08,479 --> 00:26:09,719
Cai Yan was adept in devout discipline

552
00:26:10,640 --> 00:26:12,079
and was coronated by the Emperor.

553
00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:19,040
All right.

554
00:26:19,920 --> 00:26:20,800
We're meeting Shen Yan.

555
00:26:21,079 --> 00:26:22,119
It seems like my wife

556
00:26:22,680 --> 00:26:24,160
is going to make history.

557
00:26:25,439 --> 00:26:26,239
Meet Shen Yan?

558
00:26:26,880 --> 00:26:27,400
Hold on.

559
00:26:28,079 --> 00:26:28,680
Hanchen.

560
00:26:29,040 --> 00:26:30,319
Why would you meet Shen Yan?

561
00:26:30,839 --> 00:26:32,239
What did you promise Shen Yan?

562
00:26:33,479 --> 00:26:34,719
Xingzhou, hurry up.

563
00:26:35,479 --> 00:26:36,239
Lady Xie.

