682
00:30:51,560 --> 00:30:53,280
I'm sure Li'er would enjoy that.

683
00:30:54,199 --> 00:30:55,760
Can I go?

684
00:30:56,599 --> 00:30:57,079
No way.

685
00:30:57,079 --> 00:30:58,079
Of course you may.

686
00:30:58,599 --> 00:30:59,119
Also,

687
00:30:59,520 --> 00:31:01,119
for the gifts along with
the visit this time,

688
00:31:01,439 --> 00:31:03,359
I included the Mahoraga
specially for you.

689
00:31:03,920 --> 00:31:04,800
They are tributes

690
00:31:04,800 --> 00:31:06,079
supplied to the palace.

691
00:31:06,599 --> 00:31:07,280
Really?

692
00:31:07,760 --> 00:31:09,400
That can't be true.

693
00:31:09,400 --> 00:31:10,160
It's too expensive.

694
00:31:10,359 --> 00:31:11,079
We dare not accept it.

695
00:31:11,079 --> 00:31:11,920
Don't worry about it.

696
00:31:12,359 --> 00:31:13,359
I also brought over

697
00:31:13,599 --> 00:31:14,880
various jewellery and silk.

698
00:31:15,199 --> 00:31:16,880
Xiaoman has been living
under Su Family's roof.

699
00:31:17,160 --> 00:31:18,000
As her husband,

700
00:31:18,000 --> 00:31:19,119
I should express my gratitude.

701
00:31:19,680 --> 00:31:21,079
I may have to trouble you

702
00:31:21,079 --> 00:31:22,839
to select a few goods
to be delivered to Su Family

703
00:31:23,439 --> 00:31:24,319
as my token

704
00:31:24,400 --> 00:31:25,959
of gratitude for taking
care of Xiaoman.

705
00:31:26,839 --> 00:31:27,959
You're too kind.

706
00:31:29,119 --> 00:31:29,880
Sorry for the wait.

707
00:31:32,560 --> 00:31:33,479
Thank you, mother-in-law.

708
00:31:34,319 --> 00:31:35,199
You're welcome.

709
00:31:38,599 --> 00:31:39,599
Let's eat.

710
00:31:39,599 --> 00:31:40,280
All right.

711
00:31:41,199 --> 00:31:42,199
Make yourself at home.

712
00:31:43,079 --> 00:31:44,239
It's been a long time since

713
00:31:44,239 --> 00:31:45,359
