714
00:31:45,839 --> 00:31:46,319
Here.

715
00:31:46,760 --> 00:31:47,640
A toast to all of you.

716
00:31:48,160 --> 00:31:48,680
All right.

717
00:31:49,520 --> 00:31:49,959
All right.

718
00:31:59,760 --> 00:32:01,119
Let's eat.

719
