727
00:32:35,800 --> 00:32:36,520
Inspect them.

728
00:32:39,319 --> 00:32:39,880
Mother.

729
00:32:40,839 --> 00:32:42,479
Zhao Xiaoqian

730
00:32:42,800 --> 00:32:44,719
neglected his friends
after marrying a wife.

731
00:32:44,920 --> 00:32:46,439
We agreed to play a game of Polo.

732
00:32:47,040 --> 00:32:47,839
Look at him.

733
00:32:48,280 --> 00:32:49,599
He did not even show up.

734
00:32:51,000 --> 00:32:51,839
