740
00:33:03,920 --> 00:33:04,800
Quit the nonsense.

741
00:33:05,000 --> 00:33:06,000
Are you the Commandery Prince?

742
00:33:06,520 --> 00:33:08,800
No proper family would marry a
concubine before the first wife.

743
00:33:09,119 --> 00:33:10,239
He's all grown up.

744
00:33:10,239 --> 00:33:11,560
He's looking for a wife.

745
00:33:11,560 --> 00:33:12,920
