748
00:33:18,359 --> 00:33:20,680
What do you think of the daughter
of bureaucrats, Xie Family?

749
00:33:22,000 --> 00:33:22,800
Xie Ruying?

750
00:33:24,599 --> 00:33:25,199
What?

751
00:33:25,439 --> 00:33:26,959
You're asking me to marry Yan Boyang?

752
00:33:27,359 --> 00:33:29,280
Xie Xiaoman was married
to the Commandery Prince.

753
00:33:29,439 --> 00:33:30,920
Yan Boyang is but a scholar's assistant.

754
00:33:31,359 --> 00:33:32,520
Are you asking me to marry him

755
00:33:32,680 --> 00:33:33,800
to serve Xie Xiaoman?

756
00:33:34,680 --> 00:33:35,319
Ruying.

757
00:33:36,479 --> 00:33:37,839
Xie Xiaoman is just a concubine.

758
00:33:38,280 --> 00:33:40,479
In plain terms, she's just a servant.

759
00:33:40,880 --> 00:33:42,160
If you marry Yan Boyang,

760
00:33:43,160 --> 00:33:44,680
you will be the first lady

761
00:33:44,680 --> 00:33:45,959
of Yan Family.

762
00:33:45,959 --> 00:33:46,680
I refuse.

763
00:33:49,040 --> 00:33:50,520
You're acting arbitrary.

764
00:33:51,160 --> 00:33:51,800
I think

765
00:33:52,239 --> 00:33:53,959
