you to attain education.

766
00:33:56,359 --> 00:33:58,280
You're grounded from dinner today.

767
00:34:00,280 --> 00:34:00,920
Fan Su.

768
00:34:01,160 --> 00:34:02,359
Escort the lady back to her room.

769
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:05,280
Ruying.

770
00:34:05,479 --> 00:34:05,880
Ruying.

771
00:34:06,599 --> 00:34:07,079
Lady.

