00:34:32,320 --> 00:34:33,159
It's believed

785
00:34:33,360 --> 00:34:35,360
that a hero once exist
during the Tang Dynasty.

786
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:36,360
A hero?

787
00:34:36,360 --> 00:34:38,239
He conquered the south
and defeated Wang Shichong.

788
00:34:38,479 --> 00:34:39,239
Head north,

789
00:34:39,479 --> 00:34:41,199
he captured Pi Keneng.

790
00:34:42,120 --> 00:34:43,360
He crossed the seas
and conquered the east.

791
00:34:43,600 --> 00:34:44,800
The enemies surrendered.

792
00:34:45,080 --> 00:34:45,879
Emperor of Tang appeared victorious,

793
00:34:46,159 --> 00:34:47,360
forcing the enemy to retreat.

794
00:35:00,199 --> 00:35:01,360
I don't know why.

795
00:35:02,280 --> 00:35:03,560
They haven't talked all morning.

796
00:35:15,120 --> 00:35:16,239
You did me a great favour?

797
00:35:16,239 --> 00:35:16,800
It wasn't me.

798
00:35:17,760 --> 00:35:18,879
It was Congwen.

799
00:35:21,760 --> 00:35:23,280
It's the monsoon season.

800
00:35:23,560 --> 00:35:24,360
Mosquitoes will increase in numbers.

801
00:35:25,360 --> 00:35:27,159
I'll make you a sachet
to repel the bugs.

802
00:35:27,600 --> 00:35:28,360
All right?

803
00:35:36,560 --> 00:35:37,199
Good morning, Mr. Yan.

804
00:35:37,199 --> 00:35:37,639
Good morning.

805
00:35:37,639 --> 00:35:38,879
Good morning.

806
00:35:43,360 --> 00:35:43,840
Good morning.

807
00:35:43,840 --> 00:35:44,239
Good morning.

808
00:35:46,360 --> 00:35:47,199
What's going on today?

809
00:35:47,479 --> 00:35:48,600
You're in a good mood.

810
00:35:51,280 --> 00:35:52,239
There's something I'd like to find out.

811
00:35:52,760 --> 00:35:55,280
Do you know the daughter
of Xie Family, Ruying?

812
00:35:56,360 --> 00:35:57,120
What's the matter?

813
00:35:57,320 --> 00:35:58,199
Did she humiliate you?

814
00:35:58,199 --> 00:35:59,000
Shut up.

815
00:35:59,520 --> 00:36:00,520
