821
00:36:17,159 --> 00:36:17,879
Good morning.

822
00:36:18,040 --> 00:36:18,800
Good morning.

823
00:36:21,280 --> 00:36:22,120
How was the visit back to Xie Family?

824
00:36:27,280 --> 00:36:28,360
