on Mount Kunyan.

833
00:36:43,000 --> 00:36:44,120
It's particularly effective.

834
00:36:44,520 --> 00:36:46,520
You should take Zhao Xiaoqian with you.

835
00:36:47,879 --> 00:36:48,840
