837
00:36:50,879 --> 00:36:51,840
I'm not taking him with me.

838
00:36:56,320 --> 00:36:56,879
Hanchen.

839
00:36:57,040 --> 00:36:57,879
Hanchen, where are you going?

840
00:36:58,479 --> 00:36:59,800
